title: Match History--Bug?!?
body: So for the last few weeks I've been trying to see my match history online through the website, but whenever I go to the page it just stays blank. I'm not sure if anyone else is having the same problem or if it's just my computer but I hope it gets fixed.

replies.body:
This is a known bug with that page that occasionally pops up for some players. We're looking into it, but I don't have an ETA to provide on when we'll have a fix rolled out.

Let me know if you have any other questions.
Ok thank you for letting me know :) ...
